  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (COMPOUND-03 adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification is performed. Decision recorded as Accepted with Medium assurance; however, multiple credibility factors carry achievedLevel below requiredLevel, and the model form factor achieves level 1 against a required level 4, constituting a Critical gap that structurally precludes the declared Medium assurance level.",
